TipJar-sparse-array-perl-hashbased version 0.01
===============================================

An implementation of a spare array tie class based on 
a Perl hash. This module is intended as a reference
implementation for testing, and other modules providing
the same semantics but better performance will be
forthcoming later.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Nothing. In the future, BigInt support would be good, but
it isn't in place yet.

